  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3022062/" class="title-link">最喜欢屈原和信陵君</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3022062"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4154402/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4154402-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4154402/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晴耕雨读</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-28"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-28 12:58:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3022062_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  历史小说的创作是一件看起来轻巧却吃力不讨好的事情。说轻巧是因为有现成的史料，不过译成现代的语言再加些帝王将相家的八卦秘闻。说吃力不讨好是因为很多人看来写得好是历史本身的精彩，稍有差池就是“硬伤”。既要忠于史实，又要展示写作者的语言功底与才华。而《大秦帝国》...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3022062/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 0没用</span>
