      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dm555/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2963126-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dm555/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">东门之杨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-18"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-18 00:10:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4651465_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看下来，秦国是中国历史至今最遵循法制的国家 那时候的执法系统已经近乎垂直领导，不受各级官府管辖.  看下来，秦国是中国历史至今最遵循法制的国家 那时候的执法系统已经近乎垂直领导，不受各级官府管辖.

