    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5990609/" class="title-link">习惯的影响是不可忽视的 你若盛开，清风自来</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5990609"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4325479/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4325479-17.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4325479/" class="author">
